    <section id="section_vzs_t2s_d1b">
      <title>Upload Button Compatible</title>
      <p>You can choose to display an Upload button on your App that allows site visitors to upload
    text or media to an app or your library.</p>
      <p>Trending, Polls, and Storify 2 are not compatible with the Upload Button.</p>
      <p>You must set up authentication to use this feature. </p>
